					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I've been reading SCPs for more than a decade and never bothered to join. Another story made me finally get an account to upvote it, but you are the first one to make me want to reply. This was a great, simple and well written creep-out. I love how you slip in the imagery with the little (Slurp, Slurp) and his crawling on the ceiling. Nothing explicit and yet the visuals for me were totally grotesque. Maybe I am just still in the Christmas mood.</p> <p>+1 for sure.</p> 
				 	]]>
